'''Lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender''' ([[LGBT]]) people in [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], Brazil enjoy many of the same legal protections available to non-LGBT people. Homosexuality is legal in the state.

==Recognition of same-sex unions==

On 17 April 2013, The ''General Magistrate of Justice'' of [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]], Judge Valmir de Oliveira Silva, published a legal ruling authorizing same-sex marriage in the state if local judges agree. Same sex weddings are poised to begin in the coming days.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/rio-de-janeiro-state-legalizes-gay-marriage190413|title=Rio de Janeiro state legalizes gay marriage|date=17 April 2013|accessdate= 22 April 2013}}.</ref> According to the ruling (25/2013), a couples' request must be registered by civil registry officers, who have to give 15 days for the district to decide if they agree. If they don't agree, the marriage cannot proceed.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://acapa.virgula.uol.com.br/politica/mais-um!-rio-de-janeiro-aprova-o-casamento-gay-lei-ja-esta-em-vigor-no-estado/2/14/22027|title=Rio de Janeiro facilita casamento gay em todo estado; uniões ainda passam por aval de juiz|accessdate=23 April 2013|date=19 April 2013|work=Acapa|quote=O pedido então será encaminhado ao juiz da comarca responsável, que decidirá sobre cada caso}}</ref>

==LGBT adoption==
* '''August 24, 2007''' - the Justice of the city of [[Rio de Janeiro]] authorized the adoption of a child by a [[Same-sex couple|lesbian couple]].<ref>[http://www.direitohomoafetivo.com.br/uploads_jurisprudencia/%33%39%33%2E%70%64%66 Adoption by same-sex couple in Rio de Janeiro {{pt icon}}]</ref>
* '''May 21, 2009''' - the Justice of the city of [[Rio de Janeiro]] authorized the adoption of two children by a [[Same-sex couple|lesbian couple]].<ref>[http://www.direitohomoafetivo.com.br/uploads_jurisprudencia/%37%36%33%2E%70%64%66 Adoption by same-sex couple in Rio de Janeiro {{pt icon}}]</ref>
* '''February 22, 2010''' - the Justice of the city of [[Rio de Janeiro]], [[Rio de Janeiro (state)|Rio de Janeiro]] authorized the adoption of a child by a [[Same-sex couple|lesbian couple]].<ref>[http://www.direitohomoafetivo.com.br/uploads_jurisprudencia/%36%34%38%2E%70%64%66 Adoption by same-sex couple in Rio de Janeiro {{pt icon}}]</ref>{{Clarify|date=April 2013}}

